st capped player in the history of Belarus]]\n[[File:Maksim Romaschenko.jpg|200px|thumb|right|Maksim Romaschenko is [[List of top international association football goal scorers by country|the top scorer]] in the history of Belarus with 20 goals]]\n\n===Most capped players===\nCurrently active players are listed in '''bold'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!width=40|Rank\n!width=160|Player\n!width=40|Caps\n!width=40|Goals\n!width=80|Years\n|-\n|1||align=\"left\"|[[Alyaksandr Kulchy]]||102||5||1996\u20132012\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2||align=\"left\"|[[Alexander Hleb]]||80||6||2001\u20132019\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Sergei Gurenko]]||80||3||1994\u20132006\n|-\n|4||align=\"left\"|[[Sergei Kornilenko]]||78||17||2003\u20132016\n|-\n|5||align=\"left\"|[[Timofei Kalachev]]||76||10||2004\u20132016\n|-\n|6||align=\"left\"|[[Syarhey Amelyanchuk]]||74||1||2002\u20132011\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|7||align=\"left\"|'''[[Syarhey Kislyak]]'''||71||9||2009\u2013\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Syarhey Shtanyuk]]||71||3||1995\u20132007\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''[[Alyaksandr Martynovich]]'''||71||2||2009\u2013\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|10||align=\"left\"|'''[[Stanislaw Drahun]]'''||66||11||2011\u2013\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''[[Igor Shitov]]'''||66||1||2008\u2013\n|}\n[[Sergei Aleinikov]] has reached combined 81 caps and 6 goals for [[Soviet Union national football team|Soviet Union]], [[CIS national football team|CIS]] and Belarus during 1984\u20131994.\n\n===Top scorers===\nCurrently active players are listed in '''bold'''.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!width=40|Rank\n!width=150|Player\n!width=40|Goals\n!width=40|Caps\n!width=80|Years\n|-\n|1||align=\"left\"|[[Maksim Romaschenko]]||20||64||1998\u20132008\n|-\n|2||align=\"left\"|[[Sergei Kornilenko]]||17||78||2003\u20132016\n|-\n|3||align=\"left\"|[[Vitali Kutuzov]]||13||52||2002\u20132011\n|-\n|4||align=\"left\"|'''[[Vyacheslav Hleb]]'''||12||45||2004\u20132011\n|-\n|5||align=\"left\"|'''[[Stanislaw Drahun]]'''||11||66||2011\u2013\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|6||align=\"left\"|[[Raman Vasilyuk]]||10||24||2000\u20132008\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Vitali Rodionov]]||10||48||2007\u20132017\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Valyantsin Byalkevich]]||10||56||1992\u20132005\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Timofei Kalachev]]||10||76||2004\u20132016\n|-\n|10||align=\"left\"|'''[[Syarhey Kislyak]]'''||9||71||2009\u2013\n|}\n\n==Managers==\n''As of 26 February 2020''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n!Manager\n!Career\n!Games Managed\n!width=50|Wins\n!width=50|Draws\n!width=50|Loses\n!width=80|Goals\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BLR}} [[Mikhail Vergeyenko]]\n|align=center| 1992\u20131994, 1997\u20131999\n|align=center| 24\n|align=center| 2\n|align=center| 6\n|align=center| 16\n|align=center| 22\u201340\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BLR}} [[Sergei Borovsky]]\n|align=center| 1994\u20131996, 1999\u20132000\n|align=center| 26\n|align=center| 4\n|align=center| 9\n|align=center| 13\n|align=center| 21\u201343\n|-\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Eduard Malofeyev]]\n|align=center| 2000\u20132003\n|align=center| 22\n|align=center| 10\n|align=center| 5\n|align=center| 7\n|align=center| 31\u201331\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BLR}} [[Valery Streltsov]] ([[Caretaker manager (football)|caretaker]])\n|align=center| 2002\n|align=center| 1\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 1\n|align=center| 0\u20133\n|-\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Anatoly Baidachny]]\n|align=center| 2003\u20132005\n|align=center| 22\n|align=center| 10\n|align=center| 4\n|align=center| 8\n|align=center| 34\u201329\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BLR}} [[Yuri Puntus]]\n|align=center| 2006\u20132007\n|align=center| 14\n|align=center| 3\n|align=center| 4\n|align=center| 7\n|align=center| 19\u201326\n|-\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Bernd Stange]]\n|align=center| 2007\u20132011\n|align=center| 49\n|align=center| 17\n|align=center| 14\n|align=center| 18\n|align=center| 65\u201354\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BLR}} [[Georgi Kondratiev]]\n|align=center| 2011\u20132014\n|align=center| 28\n|align=center| 9\n|align=cent